Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">NIZOM</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">1-bob. Umumiy qoidalar</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Mazkur<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Nizom (keyingi o&lsquo;rinda Nizom deb ataladi) </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasining</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\"> </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">2017 yil 11 sentyabrdagi &ldquo;Jismoniy va yuridik<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>shaxslarning<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>murojaatlari<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida&rdquo;gi<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>(yangi tahriri)<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>O&lsquo;RQ-445-sonli <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Qonun</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">iga (keyingi o&lsquo;rinlarda Qonun deb ataladi) hamda O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi Vazirlar Maxkamasining 2018 yil 7 maydagi &ldquo;Davlat organlarida, davlat muassasalarida va davlat ishtirokidagi tashkilotlarda jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarining murojaatlari bilan ishlash tartibi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi Namunaviy nizomni tasdiqlash&rdquo; xaqidagi<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>341-sonli qaroriga muvofiq Sirdaryo viloyati Iqtisodiyot va sanoat bosh boshqarmasida <strong><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></strong>(keyingi o&lsquo;rinlarda Bosh boshqarma deb ataladi) jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning murojaatlari bilan ishlash tartibini belgilaydi. </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 42.55pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; mso-list: l14 level1 lfo4; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 42.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Ushbu Nizomning amal qilishi</span><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">:</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 4;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>ko&lsquo;rib chiqish tartibi ma&rsquo;muriy javobgarlik to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidaligi, fuqarolik protsessual, jinoyat-protsessual, iqtisodiy-protsessual qonun hujjatlari va boshqa amaldagi qonunchilik xujjatlari bilan belgilangan murojaatlarga;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>davlat organlarining, tashkilotlarining, shuningdek ular tarkibiy bo&lsquo;linmalarining o&lsquo;zaro yozishmalariga nisbatan tatbiq etilmaydi.<span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; background: white; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">3. Qonunga muvofiq ushbu Nizomda quyidagi asosiy tushunchalar qo&lsquo;llaniladi:<span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\"> </span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">ariza</strong> - huquqlarni, erkinliklarni va qonuniy manfaatlarni amalga oshirishda yordam ko&lsquo;rsatish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi iltimos bayon etilgan murojaat;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; background: white; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">taklif </span></strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">- davlat va jamiyat faoliyatini takomillashtirishga doir tavsiyalarni o&lsquo;z ichiga olgan murojaat;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; background: white; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">shikoyat</span></strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"> - buzilgan huquqlarni, erkinliklarni tiklash va qonuniy manfaatlarni himoya qilish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi talab bayon etilgan murojaat;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; background: white; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">elektron murojaat</span></strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"> - belgilangan tartibda axborot-kommunikatsiya texnologiyalari vositasida berilgan, shu jumladan davlat organining, tashkilotning rasmiy veb-saytiga joylashtirilgan murojaat, real vaqt rejimida axborot-kommunikatsiya texnologiyalaridan foydalangan holda berilgan og&lsquo;zaki murojaatlar bundan mustasno;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; background: white; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">takroriy murojaat</span></strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"> - ayni bir jismoniy yoki yuridik shaxsdan kelib tushgan, uning avvalgi murojaati yuzasidan qabul qilingan qaror ustidan shikoyat qilinayotgan yoki boshqacha tarzda norozilik bildirilayotgan, shuningdek, agar takroriy murojaat kelib tushgan paytga kelib qonunchilikda belgilangan ko&lsquo;rib chiqish muddati tugagan bo&lsquo;lsa, ilgarigi murojaati o&lsquo;z vaqtida ko&lsquo;rib chiqilmaganligi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida xabar qilinayotgan murojaat;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; background: white; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">anonim murojaat</span></strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"> - jismoniy shaxsning familiyasi (ismi, otasining ismi), uning yashash joyi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi ma&rsquo;lumotlar yoki yuridik shaxsning to&lsquo;liq nomi, uning joylashgan yeri (pochta manzili) to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi ma&rsquo;lumotlar ko&lsquo;rsatilmagan yoxud ular haqida yolg&lsquo;on ma&rsquo;lumotlar ko&lsquo;rsatilgan murojaat, shuningdek uni identifikatsiya qilish imkoniyatini bermaydigan elektron murojaat yoxud imzo bilan tasdiqlanmagan yozma murojaat;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; background: white; margin: 0c