i-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Murojaat etish huqukining <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">amalga oshirilishi boshqa jismoniy va </span>yuridik <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">shaxslarning huquqlarini, erkinliklarini </span>hamda <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">qonuniy manfaatlarini, shuningdek, jamiyat </span>va <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">davlat manfaatlarini buzmasligi kerak.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm -.05pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Qonunga <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">muvofik, xorijiy davlatlarning </span>jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarining, <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">fuqaroligi bo&lsquo;lmagan shaxslar O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi </span>davlat <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">organlariga, tashkilotlariga </span>va ularning <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">mansabdor shaxslariga ushbu Q</span>onunga muvofiq murojaat etish hyqyqiga <span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>ega.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 33.4pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>6. Murojaat <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">etish<strong> </strong></span>huquqidan <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">foydalanilayotganda </span>jismoniy <span style=\"m