t-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">murojaatlar elektron shaklda;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">viloyat, </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">tuman va <span style=\"background: white;\">shaharlardagi </span>O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi <span style=\"background: white;\">Prezidenti Xalq </span>qabulxonasi <span style=\"background: white;\">orqali kelib </span>tushgan murojaatlar yozma va yoki <span style=\"background: white;\">elektron </span>shaklda olib <span style=\"background: white;\">boriladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.5pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">23. Aholi </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">bilan to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ridan-to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri <span style=\"background: white;\">muloqotni tashkil etish, murojaatlarning </span>ko&lsquo;rib <span style=\"background: white;\">chiqilishi </span>ustidan <span style=\"background: white;\">tizimli monitoring </span>va <span style=\"background: white;\">nazoratni </span>amalga <span style=\"background: white;\">oshirish, shuningdek, murojaatlar </span>bilan <span style=\"background: white;\">ishlashda </span>zamonaviy <span style=\"background: white;\">ahborot-kommunikatsiya texnologiyalaridan foydalanish maqsadida bosh boshqarma va uning </span>mansabdor <span style=\"background: white;\">shaxslari </span>o&lsquo;z virtual <span style=\"background: white;\">qabulxonalarini tashkil etishi </span>mumkin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">24.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Jismoniy va yuridik <span style=\"background: white;\">shaxsning murojaatida </span>ko&lsquo;rsatilgan <span style=\"background: white;\">masalani har tomonlama </span>va o&lsquo;z <span style=\"background: white;\">vaqtida </span>hal <span style=\"background: white;\">qilish </span>maqsadida, <span style=\"background: white;\">murojaatda ko&lsquo;rsatilgan </span>masalani <span style=\"background: white;\">ko&lsquo;rib chiqish (hal qilish) bir nechta </span>davlat organlari va <span style=\"background: white;\">tashkilotlarining </span>vakolatiga kirsa, Bosh boshqarma boshqa davlat organlari va <span style=\"background: white;\">tashkilotlariga jismoniy </span>va yuridik shaxsning <span style=\"background: white;\">murojaatini kollegial </span>eshitishni <span style=\"background: white;\">o&lsquo;tkazish uchun </span>murojaat <span style=\"background: white;\">qilishga </span>haqli.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: lines-together; page-break-after: avoid; mso-outline-level: 1; margin: 9.0pt 0cm 12.9pt 0cm;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">5-bob. Murojaatlarni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish tartibi va muddatlari</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: lines-together; page-break-after: avoid; mso-outline-level: 1;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">25. Yozma va elektron (qog&lsquo;ozga bosib chiqarilgan) murojaatlar<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>- murojaatlarni</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"> <span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">ro&lsquo;yxatga olish jurnaliga tegishli yozuvlarni kiritish, nazorat kartochkasini to&lsquo;ldirish va murojaatning birinchi sahifasi quyi o&lsquo;ng qismida ro&lsquo;yxatga olish shtampini qo&lsquo;yish yo&lsquo;li bilan Bosh boshqarma Devonxonasida ro&lsquo;yxatga olinadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Murojaatlar yozma yoki elektron tarzda ro&lsquo;yxatga olinishi mumkin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Murojaatlarni ro&lsquo;yxatga olish jurnalida murojaatning tartib raqami, murojaat qilgan jismoniy shaxsning familiyasi (ismi va otasining ismi), uning yashash joyi, yuridik shaxsning nomi, uning joylashgan joyi, murojaatning qisqacha mazmuni, murojaat qabul kilingan sana, dublikat yoki murojaatlarning takroriyligi, nazoratga olinganligi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi belgi, ijrochi etib belgilangan tarkibiy bo&lsquo;linmaning nomi, sana ko&lsquo;rsatilgan holda ijro etish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi belgi ko&lsquo;rsatiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Qayd etish shtampida Bosh boshqarmaning rasmiy nomi, murojaatning kelib tushgan sanasi va qayd raqami ko&lsquo;rsatiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Murojaatlarning tartib raqamlari har yili yil boshidan yangidan xisoblanadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.95pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">26. Jismoniy shaxslar va yuridik shaxslarning vakillari Bosh boshqarmaga og&lsquo;zaki murojaat etishganda ular tomonidan taqdim qilingan yozma murojaatlar hamda boshqa materiallar qabul qilinishi va ushbu Nizomning 25-bandiga muvofiq to&lsquo;ldirilgan hisobga olish kartochkasiga ilova qilinishi kerak.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Ro&lsquo;yxatga olingan murojaatlar kelib tushgan paytidan boshlab bir ish kunidan kechikmay Bosh boshqarma rahbariyatiga, uning o&lsquo;rinbosariga kiritiladi, u masul Bosh boshqarma bo&lsquo;lim boshlig&lsquo;ini (xodimni) belgilagan holda murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish bo&lsquo;yicha rezolyusiyani (topshiriqnoma) qo&lsquo;yadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Rezolyusiya (topshiriqnoma) qo&lsquo;yilgan paytdan boshlab bir ish kuni mobaynida devonxona murojaatni ijro etuvchi sifatida belgilangan Bosh boshqarma bo&lsquo;lim boshlig&lsquo;iga (xodimga) imzo qo&lsquo;ydirgan holda beradi. Bunda ijrochi etib belgilangan Bosh boshqarma bo&lsquo;lim boshlig&lsquo;i (xodim)tomonidan ijro etish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi belgi qo&lsquo;yiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>27. Bosh boshqarmaga kelib tushgan murojaatlar ish yurituvga qabul qilinishi, bo&lsquo;ysunish tartibida Bosh boshqarmaning tuman (shaxar) bo&lsquo;limlariga (keyingi o&lsquo;rinlarda tuman (shaxar) bo&lsquo;limlari deb ataladi) yuborilishi yoki tegishliligi bo&lsquo;yicha boshqa davlat organiga, tashkilotga yuborilishi mumkin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.7pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>28.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Tuman (shaxar) bo&lsquo;limlari tomonidan <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: italic;\">ko&lsquo;rib</span> chiqilishi kerak bo&lsquo;lgan murojaatlar unga kelib tushgan kunidan boshlab besh kun muddatdan kechiktirmay xat bilan yoki tashkilotning rahbari yoki bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i o&lsquo;rinbosari tomonidan imzolangan topshiriq bilan birga yuborilishi, bu haqda murojaat qiluvchiga yozma yohud elektron shaklda xabar berilishi kerak.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.7pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>29. <span style=\"color: black; background: white; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Agar murojaatda Bosh boshqarmaning bir nechta bo&lsquo;limlariga tegishli masalalar mavjud bo&lsquo;lsa, ularning barchasi murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish bo&lsquo;yicha ijro etuvchilar etib belgilanadi. Ijro etuvchilar orasida birinchi bo&lsquo;lib <span style=\"mso-no-proof: yes;\">k</span>o&lsquo;rsatilgan Bosh boshqarma bo&lsquo;limi boshqa bo&lsquo;limlar bilan birgalikda murojaat ko&lsquo;rib chiqilishini ta&rsquo;minlaydi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.95pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>30. Murojaatni to&lsquo;liq, holisona va o&lsquo;z vaqtida ko&lsquo;rib chiqish uchun qo&lsquo;shimcha ma&rsquo;lumotlar, ma&rsquo;lumotnomalar va materiallarga zarurat paydo bo&lsquo;lgan taqdirda, mazkur murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish jarayonida murojaat etuvchidan, shuningdek, o&lsquo;z vakolatlari doirasida boshqa davlat organlaridan, boshqa tashkilotlardan va mansabdor shaxslardan qo&lsquo;shimcha axborotni so&lsquo;rab olishi mumkin. Agar axborot davlat sirini yoki qonun bilan qo&lsquo;riqlanadigan boshqa sirni tashkil etuvchi malumotlarni o&lsquo;z ichiga olgan bo&lsquo;lmasa, jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning huquqlari, erkinliklari hamda qonuniy manfaatlariga, jamiyat va davlat manfaatlariga zarar yetkazmasa, davlat organlari, tashkilotlar va ularning mansabdor shaxslari o&lsquo;zlaridan so&lsquo;ralayotgan ahborotni o&lsquo;n kun ichida taqdim etishi shart.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.7pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>31. Agar </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">chiqish jarayonida murojaatning dublikati kelib tushsa, </span>ushbu murojaat avval <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">tushgan murojaat </span>bilan <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">birgalikda </span>ko&lsquo;rib <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">chiqiladi hamda natijasi bo&lsquo;yicha yagona javob beriladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Agar murojaat dublikat murojaat ko&lsquo;rib chiqilganidan va javob yuborilganidan keyin kelib tushsa, bu xaqida bosh boshqarma murojaat etuvchini yozma tartibda xabardor qiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.5pt; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>32. Agar murojaatda o&lsquo;rtaga qo&lsquo;yilgan masalalar xo&lsquo;jalik yurituvchi sub&rsquo;ektlar faoliyatiga dahldor bo&lsquo;lsa, ularning vakillari murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqishda ishtirok etish uchun Bosh boshqarma tomonidan o&lsquo;z vakolatlari doirasida jalb etiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>Zarur hollarda murojaatlarni ko&lsquo;rib </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Batang; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;\">chiqish</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"> uchun Bosh boshqarma tomonidan tegishli mutaxassislar jalb etilishi mumkin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.7pt; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>33. Qo&lsquo;yilgan masalalarni hal etish o&lsquo;zining vakolati doirasiga kirmaydigan murojaatlar besh kun muddatdan kechiktirmay Bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i yoki uning o&lsquo;rinbosari tomonidan imzolangan xat bilan tegishli organlarga yuboriladi, bu haqda murojaat qiluvchiga yozma yohud elektron shaklda xabar qilinadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish uchun asossiz ravishda boshqa davlat organlariga, tashkilotlariga o&lsquo;tkazish yohud qarorlari yoki harakatlari (harakatsizligi) ustidan shikoyat qilinayotgan organlarga yoki mansabdor shaxslarga yuborish taqiqlanadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Agar murojaatlarda ularni tegishli organlarga yuborish uchun zarur bo&lsquo;lgan ma&rsquo;lumotlar mavjud bo&lsquo;lmasa, u holda ular besh kun muddatdan kechiktirmay asoslantirilgan tushuntirish bilan murojaat qiluvchilarga qaytariladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.25pt; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>34. Murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish jarayonida Bosh boshqarma yoki uning mansabdor shaxslari o&lsquo;z tashabbusiga ko&lsquo;ra yohud murojaat etuvchining iltimosiga ko&lsquo;ra uni eshitishni tashkil etish mumkin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Bosh boshqarma yoki uning mansabdor shaxslari murojaat etuvchiga murojaatda ko&lsquo;tarilgan masalalar bo&lsquo;yicha o&lsquo;z fikrini bildirish va murojaat bo&lsquo;yicha qo&lsquo;shimcha axborot taqdim etish imkoniyatini beradi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Zarur hollarda murojaat etuvchini eshitishga ekspertlarni, mutaxassislarni va manfaatdor tashkilotlarning vakillarini jalb etish mumkin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.5pt; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>35. Agar murojaatda joyning o&lsquo;zida o&lsquo;rganishni talab etuvchi holat bayon qilingan bo&lsquo;lsa, shuningdek, boshqa zarur xollarda murojaatni joyning o&lsquo;zida ko&lsquo;rib chiqishni ta&rsquo;minlashi mumkin. Murojaatni joyning o&lsquo;zida ko&lsquo;rib chiqish bosh boshqarma rahbariyatining topshirig&lsquo;i yoki uning roziligi bilan amalga oshiriladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.25pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>36. Murojaatni murojaat qilgan yoki boshqa shaxsning ishtirokisiz ko&lsquo;rib chiqishning imkoniyati bo&lsquo;lmaganda, ular Bosh boshqarma raxbariyati tomonidan chaqirilishi mumkin. Chaqirilgan murojaat qiluvchi kelmagan taqdirda Bosh boshqarma murojaatni uning ishtirokisiz ko&lsquo;rib chiqish mumkin emasligi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida javob xati yuboradi.</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.25pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>37. <span style=\"color: black; background: white; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Murojaatlar bilan ishlash muddatlari ular Bosh boshqarmaga kelib tushgan kundan boshlab hisoblanadi. Agar tegishli muddatning oxirgi kuni dam olish va bayram kunlariga to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri kelsa, navbatdagi ish kuni muddat tugaydigan kun hisoblanadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Elektron murojaatlar tushgan kunida qog&lsquo;ozga bosib chiqarilishi, ish vaqti tamom bo&lsquo;lgandan keyin tushgan taqdirda esa<span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>navbatdagi ish kunida qog&lsquo;ozga bosib</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"> <span style=\"color: black; background: white; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">chiqarilishi kerak.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Murojaatni ro&lsquo;yxatdan o&lsquo;tkazishni rad etishga yo&lsquo;l qo&lsquo;yilmaydi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Bosh boshqarma rahbariga yoki bunga vakolat berilgan boshqa mansabdor shaxsiga ommaviy qabullar vaqtida tushgan va joyida hal etilgan og&lsquo;zaki murojaatlarni ro&lsquo;yxatdan o&lsquo;tkazish talab qilinmaydi. Bunda jismoniy shaxsning yoki yuridik shaxs vakilining familiyasi (ismi, otasining ismi), uning yashash joyi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi ma&rsquo;lumotlar, murojaatning qisqacha mazmuni, shuningdek, uni ko&lsquo;rib <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: italic;\">chiqish</span><span style=\"mso-no-proof: yes;\"> </span>natijasi ommaviy qabul bayonnomasida ko&lsquo;rsatiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.25pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>38. Ariza yoki shikoyat masalani mazmuni bo&lsquo;yicha hal etishi shart bo&lsquo;lgan murojaat kelib tushgan kundan e&rsquo;tiboran o&lsquo;n besh kun mobaynida, ko&lsquo;shimcha o&lsquo;rganish va (yoki) tekshirish, qo&lsquo;shimcha xujjatlarni so&lsquo;rab olish talab etilganda esa bir oygacha bo&lsquo;lgan muddatda <span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>ko&lsquo;rib chiqiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Ariza va shikoyatlarni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish uchun tekshirish o&lsquo;tkazish, qo&lsquo;shimcha materiallarni so&lsquo;rab olish yohud boshqa chora-tadbirlar ko&lsquo;rish zarur bo&lsquo;lgan hollarda, ularni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish muddatlari bosh boshqarma rahbariyati tomonidan, istisno tariqasida, ko&lsquo;pi bilan bir oyga uzaytirilishi mumkin, bu haqida murojaat etuvchiga xabar qilinadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.5pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>39. Taklif bosh boshqarmaga kelib tushgan kundan e&rsquo;tiboran bir oygacha bo&lsquo;lgan muddatda ko&lsquo;rib chiqiladi, qo&lsquo;shimcha o&lsquo;rganishni talab etadigan takliflar bundan mustasno, bu haqda taklifni kiritgan jismoniy yoki yuridik shaxsga o&lsquo;n kun muddatda yozma shaklda xabar qilinadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 1.0cm; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>40. Ayrim hollarda Bosh boshqarma raxbari yoki uning o&lsquo;rinbosari murojaatlarni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish muddatlarini qisqartirishlari mumkin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 1.0cm; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>41. Murojaatlarni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish natijalari bo&lsquo;yicha Bosh boshqarma tomonidan tegishli qaror qabul qilinadi, bu haqda darxol yozma yohud elektron shaklda murojaat qiluvchiga xabar beriladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Murojaatni qoniqtirmaslik to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi qarorni;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Bosh boshqarmada &ndash; boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i, uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlari qabul qiladi;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>Murojaatga javob xatida murojaatda ko&lsquo;rsatilgan har bir masala bo&lsquo;yicha vajlarni rad qiluvchi yoki tasdiqlovchi aniq asoslar (zaruriyatga qarab konun hujjatlari normalariga havola qilingan holda) bo&lsquo;lishi kerak.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.25pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">42. Murojaatga javob xati boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i va uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlari tomonidan imzolanadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Murojaatlarga javob xati, mumkin qadar, murojaat etilgan tilda bayon qilinadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.7pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">43. Jismoniy yoki yuridik shaxslar jamoa bo&lsquo;lib murojaat qilgan taqdirda, ularning murojaatlari Qonun talablari va mazkur Nizomga muvofiq ko&lsquo;rib chiqiladi. <span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>Bunda murojaatga javob murojaat qilganlarning ro&lsquo;yxatida birinchi bo&lsquo;lib ko&lsquo;rsatilgan shaxsga yoki, ularning talabiga ko&lsquo;ra, boshqa shaxsga yuboriladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.7pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">44. Jismoniy yoki yuridik shaxsning iltimosiga ko&lsquo;pa murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqishda murojaatga </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">javobni <span style=\"background: white; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">uning mazmunini o&lsquo;zgartirmasdan tushuntirishi, shuningdek yo&lsquo;l </span>qo&lsquo;yilgan <span style=\"background: white; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">xatolar va arifmetik xatolarni o&lsquo;z tashabbusiga ko&lsquo;ra yoki murojaat qiluvchining iltimosiga ko&lsquo;ra, murojaatga javobning </span>mazmuniga <span style=\"background: white; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">daxl qilmagan holda tuzatishi </span>shart.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Murojaat qiluvchining murojaatga javobni tushuntirish va uni tuzatish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi iltimosi u kelib tushgan kundan e&rsquo;tiboran <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: italic;\">10<strong> </strong></span>kun ichida ko&lsquo;rib chiqiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 1.0cm; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>45. Murojaat, unda ko&lsquo;tarilgan barcha masalalar Qonun talablariga muvofiq ko&lsquo;rib chiqilgan va murojaat qiluvchiga tegishli javob yuborilgan taqdirda ko&lsquo;rib chiqilgan hisoblanadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Murojaat qiluvchiga javob yuborilgan kun murojaatni </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">ko&lsquo;rib <span style=\"background: white; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">chiqish tugallangan kun hisoblanadi, bu xakda Devonxona murojaatlarni ro&lsquo;yxatga olish jurnaliga va hisobga olish kartochkasiga belgi qo&lsquo;yadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.5pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>46. Ko&lsquo;rib chiqilgan murojaatlarni va ular bilan bog&lsquo;lik materiallarni saqlash Devonxonada belgilangan tartibda amalga oshiriladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.5pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 1.0pt;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;\">6</span><strong><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">-</span></em></strong><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">bob. Murojaatlarni ko&lsquo;rmay qoldirish va </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 1.0pt;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">ko&lsquo;rib chiqishni tugatish</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 1.0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>47. Quyidagi murojaatlar ko&lsquo;rib chiqilmaydi:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">anonim murojaatlar;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning vakillari orqali berilgan murojaatlar, ularning vakolatini tasdiqlovchi xujjatlar mavjud bo&lsquo;lmagan taqdirda;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Konunda belgilangan<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>boshqa talablarga muvofiq bo&lsquo;lmagan murojaatlar.<span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 1.0cm; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>48. Murojaatni anonim deb e&rsquo;tirof etish Bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i birinchi o&lsquo;rinbosari tomonidan amalga oshiriladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 2.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Murojaat anonim deb z&rsquo;tirof etilganda bu haqda hulosa tuziladi. Hulosada murojaatni anonim deb e&rsquo;tirof etish uchun asoslar ko&lsquo;rsatiladi. Murojaatni anonim deb e&rsquo;tirof etish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;isidagi hulosa bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i tomonidan tasdiqlanadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 2.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Bosh boshqarmaning ishonch telefonlari</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">ga tushgan murojaatlar <span style=\"background: white;\">Qonunda nazarda tutilgan tartibda </span>anonim deb e&rsquo;tirof etilishi mumkin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 2.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Anonim deb e&rsquo;tirof etilgan murojaatlar hulosa tasdiqlangan paytdan boshlab nazoratdan yoki ijrodan olinadi va ko&lsquo;rib chiqilmaydi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 38.7pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">49. Jismoniy </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">va <span style=\"background: white;\">yuridik shaxslarning vakillari orqali berilgan </span>murojaatlar kelib <span style=\"background: white;\">tushganda, Devonxona bosh mutaxassisi</span> ularning <span style=\"background: white;\">vakolatlarini tasdiqlaydigan xujjatlar mavjudligini tekshiradi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 2.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Agar murojaatda jismoniy va yuridik shaxs vakilining vakolatlarini tasdiqlaydigan xujjatlar mavjud bo&lsquo;lmasa, bu haqda <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Devonxona bosh mutaxassisi</span></span><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"> </span></strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">tomonidan tasdiqlanadigan hulosa tuziladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 2.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Jismoniy va yuridik shaxs vakilining vakolatlarini tasdiqlaydigan xujjatlar mavjud emasligi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi hulosa tasdiqlangan paytdan boshlab ushbu murojaat ko&lsquo;rib chiqilmaydi, bu haqda murojaat qiluvchi yozma ravishda habardor qilinadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 1.0cm; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>50. Murojaatlar ko&lsquo;rmay qoldirilganda tegishli hulosa tuziladi, u Bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i yoki uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlari tomonidan tasdiqlanadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 2.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Jismoniy va yuridik shaxs vakilining vakolatini tasdiqlovchi xujjatlar mavjud emasligi sababli murojaatlar ko&lsquo;rmay qoldirilganligi tug&lsquo;risida murojaat qiluvchi tegishli tartibda xabardor qilinadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 38.5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 26.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">51. Murojaatlarni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish quyidagi xollarda tugatiladi:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 2.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">agar <span style=\"background: white;\">takroriy murojaatlarda </span>yangi <span style=\"background: white;\">vajlar </span>yoki <span style=\"background: white;\">yangidan ochilgan holatlar keltirilmagan </span>bo&lsquo;lsa, ilgarigi murojaat <span style=\"background: white;\">materiallarida esa tekshiruvlarning to&lsquo;la-to&lsquo;kis materiallari </span>mavjud bo&lsquo;lsa va murojaat <span style=\"background: white;\">qiluvchiga belgilangan </span>tartibda <span style=\"background: white;\">javoblar berilgan </span>bo&lsquo;lsa;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 2.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">agar murojaat qiluvchi o&lsquo;z murojaatini belgilangan tartibda chaqirib olgan bo&lsquo;lsa yoki uni ko&lsquo;rib chiqishni tugatash to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida iltimos qilgan bo&lsquo;lsa;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 2.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">yashash joyi, turgan joyi (pochta manzili), elektron pochta manzili yoki boshqa rekvizitlari o&lsquo;zgartirilganligi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida o&lsquo;z vaqtida habardor qilmaganligi tufayli chaqirishning imkoni yo&lsquo;qligi sababli murojaatni murojaat qiluvchining ishtirokisiz ko&lsquo;rib chiqish imkoniyati bo&lsquo;lmaganda;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 2.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">murojaatni </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">murojaat <span style=\"background: white;\">qiluvchining </span>ishtirokisiz ko&lsquo;rib chiqish <span style=\"background: white;\">imkoniyati </span>mavjud emasligi sababli, Bosh boshqarma<span style=\"background: white;\"> tomonidan chaqirilgan </span>murojaat qiluvchi <span style=\"background: white;\">kelmay kolgan taqdirda;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 2.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">agar murojaat qiluvchi jismoniy shaxs vafot etganidan so&lsquo;ng murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish huquqiy vorislikka yo&lsquo;l qo&lsquo;ymasa.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 1.0cm; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>52. Murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqishni tugagani to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi qarorni Bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i birinchi o&lsquo;rinbosari qabul qiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Takroriy murojaatni </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">ko&lsquo;rib <span style=\"background: white;\">chi<span style=\"mso-no-proof: yes;\">qish</span>da ushbu Nizomning </span>51-band <span style=\"background: white;\">ikkinchi xatboshisiga muvofiq tugatilganda, murojaat qiluvchi </span>takroriy <span style=\"background: white;\">murojaatning</span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"> <span style=\"color: black;\">asossizligi va ushbu <span style=\"background: white;\">masala </span>yuzasidan u <span style=\"background: white;\">bilan </span>yozishmalar <span style=\"background: white;\">tugatilishi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida </span>yozma <span style=\"background: white;\">ravishda habardor qilinadi. Yozishmalar </span>olib borish tugatilgan <span style=\"background: white;\">murojaat </span>qiluvchidan takroriy murojaat <span style=\"background: white;\">kelib tushgan taqdirda, bunday </span>murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib <span style=\"background: white;\">chiqish </span>murojaat <span style=\"background: white;\">qiluvchini </span>bu haqda xabardor <span style=\"background: white;\">qilmasdan tugatiladi.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish <span style=\"background: white;\">uni chaqirib olish </span>to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi <span style=\"background: white;\">ariza bo&lsquo;yicha </span>tugatilganda murojaat murojaat qiluvchiga <span style=\"background: white;\">xat orqali uch </span>kun <span style=\"background: white;\">ichida qaytariladi. </span>Murojaatni <span style=\"background: white;\">chaqirib </span>olish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi ariza <span style=\"background: white;\">qonun buzilishlarini aniqlash </span>va <span style=\"background: white;\">bartaraf etish </span>yuzasidan <span style=\"background: white;\">chora-tadbirlar ko&lsquo;rishni istisno etmaydi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Murojaat qiluvchi <span style=\"background: white;\">chaqirilgan jismoniy shaxsning </span>yoki <span style=\"background: white;\">yuridik </span>shaxs <span style=\"background: white;\">vakilining kelmay qolganligi sababli </span>murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqishni <span style=\"background: white;\">tugatish </span>to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida <span style=\"background: white;\">tegishli tartibda </span>xabardor <span style=\"background: white;\">qilinadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">7-bob. </span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Jismoniy<span style=\"background: white;\"> shaxslarni </span>va <span style=\"background: white;\">yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini </span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">qabul <span style=\"background: white;\">qilishni tashkil </span>etish</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.25pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">53. Bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i va <span style=\"background: white;\">uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlari tomonidan </span>jismoniy <span style=\"background: white;\">shaxslarni </span>va yuridik shaxslarning <span style=\"background: white;\">vakillarini </span>qabul <span style=\"background: white;\">qilish tashkil etiladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i va <span style=\"background: white;\">uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlari </span>tomonidan jismoniy va yuridik <span style=\"background: white;\">shaxslar vakillarining </span>sayyor <span style=\"background: white;\">qabullari, </span>shuningdek <span style=\"background: white;\">ommaviy qabullar tashkil etilishi mumkin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>55. Bosh boshkarma boshligining jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini joylarda sayyor kabul kilish buyicha jadvallari (yillik yoki yarim yillik) ishlab chikilib, mos ravishda Sirdaryo viloyat xokimi tomonidan tasdiklanadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 1.0cm; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>54. Bosh boshqarmada j</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">ismoniy va yuridik <span style=\"background: white;\">shaxslarning </span>vakillarini qabul <span style=\"background: white;\">qilish belgilangan </span>kun va <span style=\"background: white;\">soatlarda, </span>qabul qilish jadvaliga <span style=\"background: white;\">muvofiq o&lsquo;tkaziladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Qabul qilish jadvali </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">va <span style=\"background: white;\">uni o&lsquo;tkazish </span>vaqti, <span style=\"background: white;\">joyi </span>hamda <span style=\"background: white;\">qabulga oldindan </span>yozilish <span style=\"background: white;\">to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi ahborot, </span>qabul qilish <span style=\"background: white;\">tartibi ularni Bosh boshkarmaning rasmiy veb-saytlarida e&rsquo;lon kilish, shuningdek, Bosh boshkarmaning ma&rsquo;muriy binosida hamda kirishi </span>mumkin b<span style=\"background: white;\">o&lsquo;lgan </span>joylardagi <span style=\"background: white;\">stendlarga </span>yoki boshqa texnik vositalarga <span style=\"background: white;\">joylashtirish orqali manfaatdor </span>shahslar <span style=\"background: white;\">e&rsquo;tiboriga </span>yetkaziladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Bosh boshqarma hamda fuqarolarning o&lsquo;zini o&lsquo;zi<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>boshqarish organlari tomonidan o&lsquo;tkaziladigan sayyor va ommaviy qabullar<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida bir xafta oldin aholi bilan targ&lsquo;ibot ishlari amalga oshiriladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.25pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">55. Bosh boshqarmada<span style=\"background: white;\"> jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini </span>qabul qilish uchun <span style=\"background: white;\">alohida xona ajratiladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Shaxsiy </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">qabul <span style=\"background: white;\">davomida Bosh boshqarma rahbariyatining qaroriga </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>va murojaat <span style=\"background: white;\">etuvchiga </span>bu xaqda habar <span style=\"background: white;\">bergan holda maxsus </span>texnika <span style=\"background: white;\">vositalari </span>(audio va <span style=\"background: white;\">videoyozuv, </span>shuniigdek <span style=\"background: white;\">fotosuratga </span>olish) <span style=\"background: white;\">qo&lsquo;llanilishi mumkin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.7pt; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">56. Og&lsquo;zaki murojaatlar bilan kelgan jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning vakillari Bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i va uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlari tomonidan qabul qilinadi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Murojaat </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">qiluvchining <span style=\"background: white;\">shaxsini tasdiqlaydigan xujjatlar tekshirilgandan keyin </span>ushbu <span style=\"background: white;\">Nizomning </span>2-ilovasiga <span style=\"background: white;\">muvofiq shakl </span>bo&lsquo;yicha hisobga olish <span style=\"background: white;\">kartochkasi to&lsquo;l</span>diriladi. Hisobga olish <span style=\"background: white;\">kartochkasi </span>og&lsquo;zaki murojaat <span style=\"background: white;\">sifatida ro&lsquo;yxatga olinadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.35pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">57. Jismoniy <span style=\"background: white;\">shaxs og&lsquo;zaki murojaat etayotganda </span>o&lsquo;z <span style=\"background: white;\">shaxsini tasdiqlovchi xujjatni, yuridik shaxsning vakili esa </span>o&lsquo;z <span style=\"background: white;\">vakolatlarini tasdiqlaydigan </span>va <span style=\"background: white;\">o&lsquo;z </span>shahsini tasdiqlovchi <span style=\"background: white;\">hujjatni ko&lsquo;rsatishi kerak, ommaviy </span>qabul <span style=\"background: white;\">vaqtida kelib tushgan murojaatlar bundan mustasno.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">Og&lsquo;zaki murojaatlar real <span style=\"background: white;\">vaqt rejimida <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">axborot-kommunikatsiya<strong> </strong></span>texnologiyalaridan foydalangan holda, shu jumladan bosh boshqarmaning ishonch telefonlari orqali ham berilishi mumkin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 1.0cm; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>58. Devonxona qabulga kelgan jismoniy shaxslarni </span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\">va <span style=\"background: white;\">yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini </span>qabul <span style=\"background: white;\">qilish, shuningdek </span>jismoniy shaxslarni va yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini qabul <span style=\"background: white;\">qilish </span>bilan bog&lsquo;liq <span style=\"background: white;\">ishlarni tashkil etadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 36.65pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>59. Bosh boshqarmada jismoniy shaxslarning va yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini qabul qilish <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Devonxona</span> yoki tegishli Bosh boshqarma bo&lsquo;limi xodimlari ishtirokida amalga oshiriladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 1.0cm; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>60. Jismoniy shaxslarni va yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini qabul qiluvchi rahbar yoki vakolatli shaxsning ko&lsquo;rsatmasi bo&lsquo;yicha Bosh boshqarmaning boshqa xodimlari ham qabul qilish jarayoniga jalb etilishi mumkin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.55pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>61. Agar jismoniy shaxslarni va yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini <span style=\"background: white;\">shaxsiy, sayyor va ommaviy <span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Batang; color: black; background: white; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;\">qabul</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"> qilish paytida <span style=\"background: white;\">murojaatda </span>bayon <span style=\"background: white;\">qilingan masalalarni </span>hal <span style=\"background: white;\">etish Bosh boshqarmaning vakolatiga <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">kirmasligi </span>aniqlangan taqdirda, </span>ularga murojaatda bayon <span style=\"background: white;\">qilingan </span>masalalarni <span style=\"background: white;\">hal </span>etish <span style=\"background: white;\">uchun qaysi organga yoki tashkilotga murojaat qilish kerakligi tushuntiriladi. </span>Bunda jismoniy shaxslarning va yuridik shaxslar <span style=\"background: white;\">vakillarining talabi </span>bilan <span style=\"background: white;\">bu </span>xaqda yozma <span style=\"background: white;\">shaklda javob beriladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.35pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>62. Jismoniy shaxslarning va yuridik shaxslar vakillarining <span style=\"background: white;\">sayyor<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>qabullari, </span>shuningdek ommaviy qabullari,<strong><span style=\"background: white;\"> </span></strong><span style=\"background: white;\">zarur </span>bo&lsquo;lgan <span style=\"background: white;\">hollarda, </span>qabul <span style=\"background: white;\">qilish jadvallaridan tashqari </span>o&lsquo;tkazilishi mumkin. Ommaviy qabul <span style=\"background: white;\">hovlilarga (kvartiralarga), boshqa binolarga va joylarga birma-bir kirib chiqish orqali ham o&lsquo;tkazilishi mumkin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.2pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>63. Jismoniy shaxslar va yuridik shaxslar <span style=\"background: white;\">vakillarining </span>sayyor <span style=\"background: white;\">shaxsiy </span>qabullar <span style=\"background: white;\">vaqtida berilgan og&lsquo;zaki murojaat ushbu Nizomning 57-bandiga </span>muvofiq <span style=\"background: white;\">rasmiylashtiriladi </span>va ro&lsquo;yxatga <span style=\"background: white;\">olinadi hamda belgilangan<strong> </strong>tartibda ko&lsquo;rib </span>chiqiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.2pt; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: RU;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>63. Joylarda uchrashuvlarni o&lsquo;tkazish mavzusiga mamlakatning strategik maqsadlarini amalga oshirishda<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>ustuvor bo&lsquo;lgan fuqarolik jamiyatini va xalq bilan ochiq muloqotni rivojlantirish, inson xuquq va manfaatlarini, davlat va mahalliy ijro etuvchi hokimiyat organlari faoliyatinining ochiqligini ta&rsquo;minlash, amalga oshirilayotgan islohotlarning tub mohiyati va hududlarni kompleks rivojlantirishning istiqbolli rejalari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida aholiga yetkazish, joylardagi tizimli muammolarni aniqlash va ularning yechimlarini topish, jismoniy shaxslar va yuridik shaxslar vakillarini qabul qilish, murojaatlarni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish kabi dolzarb masalalar kiritilishi lozim.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: none; tab-stops: 37.2pt; margi