 style=\"text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Murojaat qiluvchi&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">chaqirilgan jismoniy shaxsning&nbsp;</span>yoki&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">yuridik&nbsp;</span>shaxs&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">vakilining kelmay qolganligi sababli&nbsp;</span>murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqishni&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">tugatish&nbsp;</span>to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">tegishli tartibda&nbsp;</span>xabardor&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qilinadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\" align=\"center\"><span class=\"1\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">7-bob.&nbsp;</span></strong></span><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Jismoniy<span class=\"1\">&nbsp;shaxslarni&nbsp;</span>va&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">qabul&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qilishni tashkil&nbsp;</span>etish</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.25pt; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">53. Bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i va&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlari tomonidan&nbsp;</span>jismoniy&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">shaxslarni&nbsp;</span>va yuridik shaxslarning&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">vakillarini&nbsp;</span>qabul&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qilish tashkil etiladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i va&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlari&nbsp;</span>tomonidan jismoniy va yuridik&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">shaxslar vakillarining&nbsp;</span>sayyor&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qabullari,&nbsp;</span>shuningdek&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">ommaviy qabullar tashkil etilishi mumkin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;55. Bosh boshkarma boshligining jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini joylarda sayyor kabul kilish buyicha jadvallari (yillik yoki yarim yillik) ishlab chikilib, mos ravishda Sirdaryo viloyat xokimi tomonidan tasdiklanadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 1.0cm; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.15pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;54. Bosh boshqarmada j</span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">ismoniy va yuridik&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">shaxslarning&nbsp;</span>vakillarini qabul&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qilish belgilangan&nbsp;</span>kun va&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">soatlarda,&nbsp;</span>qabul qilish jadvaliga&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">muvofiq o&lsquo;tkaziladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Qabul qilish jadvali&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">va&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">uni o&lsquo;tkazish&nbsp;</span>vaqti,&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">joyi&nbsp;</span>hamda&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qabulga oldindan&nbsp;</span>yozilish&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi ahborot,&nbsp;</span>qabul qilish&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">tartibi ularni Bosh boshkarmaning rasmiy veb-saytlarida e&rsquo;lon kilish, shuningdek, Bosh boshkarmaning ma&rsquo;muriy binosida hamda kirishi&nbsp;</span>mumkin b<span class=\"1\">o&lsquo;lgan&nbsp;</span>joylardagi&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">stendlarga&nbsp;</span>yoki boshqa texnik vositalarga&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">joylashtirish orqali manfaatdor&nbsp;</span>shahslar&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">e&rsquo;tiboriga&nbsp;</span>yetkaziladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Bosh boshqarma hamda fuqarolarning o&lsquo;zini o&lsquo;zi&nbsp;&nbsp;boshqarish organlari tomonidan o&lsquo;tkaziladigan sayyor va ommaviy qabullar&nbsp;&nbsp;to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida bir xafta oldin aholi bilan targ&lsquo;ibot ishlari amalga oshiriladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.25pt; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">55. Bosh boshqarmada<span class=\"1\">&nbsp;jismoniy&nbsp;</span><span class=\"Candara1\"><span style=\"mso-ansi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">va&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"1\">yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini&nbsp;</span>qabul qilish uchun&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">alohida xona ajratiladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Shaxsiy&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">qabul&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">davomida Bosh boshqarma rahbariyatining qaroriga&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;va murojaat&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">etuvchiga&nbsp;</span>bu xaqda habar&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">bergan holda maxsus&nbsp;</span>texnika&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">vositalari&nbsp;</span>(audio va&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">videoyozuv,&nbsp;</span>shuniigdek&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">fotosuratga&nbsp;</span>olish)&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qo&lsquo;llanilishi mumkin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"210\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.7pt; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">56. Og&lsquo;zaki&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"21\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">murojaatlar&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">bilan&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"21\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">kelgan&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"21\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">vakillari Bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i va uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlari t</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">omonidan&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"21\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">qabul&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">qilinadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"text-indent: 23.0pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Murojaat&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">qiluvchining&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">shaxsini tasdiqlaydigan xujjatlar tekshirilgandan keyin&nbsp;</span>ushbu&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">Nizomning&nbsp;</span>2-ilovasiga&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">muvofiq shakl&nbsp;</span>bo&lsquo;yicha hisobga olish&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">kartochkasi to&lsquo;l</span>diriladi. Hisobga olish&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">kartochkasi&nbsp;</span>og&lsquo;zaki murojaat&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">sifatida ro&lsquo;yxatga olinadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.35pt; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">57. Jismoniy&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">shaxs og&lsquo;zaki murojaat etayotganda&nbsp;</span>o&lsquo;z&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">shaxsini tasdiqlovchi xujjatni, yuridik shaxsning vakili esa&nbsp;</span>o&lsquo;z&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">vakolatlarini tasdiqlaydigan&nbsp;</span>va&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">o&lsquo;z&nbsp;</span>shahsini tasdiqlovchi&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">hujjatni ko&lsquo;rsatishi kerak, ommaviy&nbsp;</span>qabul&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">vaqtida kelib tushgan murojaatlar bundan mustasno.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Og&lsquo;zaki murojaatlar real&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">vaqt rejimida&nbsp;</span><span class=\"a\">axborot-kommunikatsiya</span><span class=\"a\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"1\">texnologiyalaridan foydalangan holda, shu jumladan bosh boshqarmaning ishonch telefonlari orqali ham berilishi mumkin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 1.0cm; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;58. Devonxona qabulga kelgan jismoniy shaxslarni&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">va&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini&nbsp;</span>qabul&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qilish, shuningdek&nbsp;</span>jismoniy shaxslarni va yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini qabul&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qilish&nbsp;</span>bilan bog&lsquo;liq&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">ishlarni tashkil etadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"210\" style=\"margin-right: 2.0pt; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 36.65pt; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;59. Bosh boshqarmada jismoniy shaxslarning va yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"21\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">qabul qilish&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Devonxona</span></span><span class=\"24\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;yoki&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"21\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">tegishli Bosh boshqarma bo&lsquo;limi&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">xodimlari&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"21\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">ishtirokida&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">amalga&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"24\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">oshiriladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"210\" style=\"margin-right: 2.0pt; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 1.0cm; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;60. Jismoniy shaxslarni va yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini qabul qiluvchi rahbar yoki&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"21\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">vakolatli&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">shaxsning ko&lsquo;rsatmasi bo&lsquo;yicha Bosh boshqarmaning&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"21\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">boshqa xodimlari&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">ham qabul qilish&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"21\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">jarayoniga jalb etilishi&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">mumkin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.55pt; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;61. Agar jismoniy shaxslarni va yuridik shaxslarning vakillarini&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">shaxsiy, sayyor va ommaviy&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"a1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-style: normal; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;\">qabul</span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;qilish paytida&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">murojaatda&nbsp;</span>bayon&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qilingan masalalarni&nbsp;</span>hal&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">etish Bosh boshqarmaning vakolatiga&nbsp;</span><span class=\"a\">kirmasligi&nbsp;</span><span class=\"1\">aniqlangan taqdirda,&nbsp;</span>ularga murojaatda bayon&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qilingan&nbsp;</span>masalalarni&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">hal&nbsp;</span>etish&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">uchun qaysi organga yoki tashkilotga murojaat qilish kerakligi tushuntiriladi.&nbsp;</span>Bunda jismoniy shaxslarning va yuridik shaxslar&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">vakillarining talabi&nbsp;</span>bilan&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">bu&nbsp;</span>xaqda yozma&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">shaklda javob beriladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.35pt; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;62. Jismoniy shaxslarning va yuridik shaxslar vakillarining&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">sayyor&nbsp;&nbsp;qabullari,&nbsp;</span>shuningdek ommaviy qabullari,<span class=\"a\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"1\">zarur&nbsp;</span>bo&lsquo;lgan&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">hollarda,&nbsp;</span>qabul&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">qilish jadvallaridan tashqari&nbsp;</span>o&lsquo;tkazilishi mumkin. Ommaviy qabul&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">hovlilarga (kvartiralarga), boshqa binolarga va joylarga birma-bir kirib chiqish orqali ham o&lsquo;tkazilishi mumkin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.2pt; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;63. Jismoniy shaxslar va yuridik shaxslar&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">vakillarining&nbsp;</span>sayyor&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">shaxsiy&nbsp;</span>qabullar&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">vaqtida berilgan og&lsquo;zaki murojaat ushbu Nizomning 57-bandiga&nbsp;</span>muvofiq&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">rasmiylashtiriladi&nbsp;</span>va ro&lsquo;yxatga&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">olinadi hamda belgilangan</span><span class=\"a\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"1\">tartibda ko&lsquo;rib&nbsp;</span>chiqiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.2pt; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;63. Joylarda uchrashuvlarni o&lsquo;tkazish mavzusiga mamlakatning strategik maqsadlarini amalga oshirishda&nbsp;&nbsp;ustuvor bo&lsquo;lgan fuqarolik jamiyatini va xalq bilan ochiq muloqotni rivojlantirish, inson xuquq va manfaatlarini, davlat va mahalliy ijro etuvchi hokimiyat organlari faoliyatinining ochiqligini ta&rsquo;minlash, amalga oshirilayotgan islohotlarning tub mohiyati va hududlarni kompleks rivojlantirishning istiqbolli rejalari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida aholiga yetkazish, joylardagi tizimli muammolarni aniqlash va ularning yechimlarini topish, jismoniy shaxslar va yuridik shaxslar vakillarini qabul qilish, murojaatlarni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish kabi dolzarb masalalar kiritilishi lozim.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.2pt; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;64. Sayyor va ommaviy qabulni o&lsquo;tkazish natijalari bo&lsquo;yicha tegishli bayon to&lsquo;ldiriladi, chora-tadbirlar rejasi ishlab chiqiladi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.2pt; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt 9.7pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;64. Ommaviy qabullar&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">vaqtida Bosh boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;iga yoki uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlariga</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">kelib&nbsp;</span>tushgan va&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">joyida hal etilgan og&lsquo;zaki murojaatlarga&nbsp;</span>yozma javob&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">yoki elektron shakldagi&nbsp;</span>javob&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">talab&nbsp;</span>etilmaydi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 9.0pt 13.0pt 9.95pt 0cm;\" align=\"center\"><span class=\"1\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">8-bob.&nbsp;</span></strong></span><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Jismoniy va yuridik&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">shaxslarning huquqlari</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm -2.5pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">65. Murojaatlar Bosh&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i&nbsp;&nbsp;yoki&nbsp;&nbsp;uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlari&nbsp;</span>tomonidan&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">ko&lsquo;rib chiqilayotganda&nbsp;</span>jismoniy va yuridik&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">shaxslar quyidagi huquqlarga&nbsp;</span>ega:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm -2.5pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">chiqishning borishi&nbsp;</span>to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">ahborot olish;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">vajlarni&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"17\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-style: normal; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;\">shaxsan</span></span><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">bayon etish va&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">tushuntirishlar berish;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">murojaatni&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">tekshirish materiallari&nbsp;</span>va&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">uni&nbsp;</span>k</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">o&lsquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">rib&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">chi</span></span><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">q</span></span><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">ish natijalari&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">bilan&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">tanishish;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">qo&lsquo;shimcha materiallar taqdim&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">etish yoki&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">bunday materiallarni&nbsp;</span>boshqa&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">organlardan&nbsp;</span>talab qilib olish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida&nbsp;<span class=\"1\">iltimos qilish;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"210\" style=\"margin-left: 1.0pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;advokat&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"21\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">yordamidan&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">foydalanish;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqishni to&lsquo;xtatish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida yohud murojaatga javobni tushuntirish va (yoki) uni tuzatish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi iltimos qilish<strong>;</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">o&lsquo;z murojaatini u ko&lsquo;rib chiqilgunga qadar&nbsp;&nbsp;va ko&lsquo;rib chiqilayotgan paytda murojaat bo&lsquo;yicha qaror qabul qilingunga qadar yozma yoki elektron shaklda ariza berish yo&lsquo;li bilan chaqirib olish;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">murojaatni qabul qilish yoki ko&lsquo;rib chiqishni qonunga xilof ravishda rad etganlik ustidan bo&lsquo;ysunuv tartibida yuqori turuvchi organga yoki bevosita sudga shikoyat qilish.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Jismoniy va yuridik shaxslar qonun hujjatlariga muvofiq boshqa huquqlarga ham ega bo&lsquo;lishi mumkin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">66. Jismoniy va yuridik shaxslar,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"1\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">boshqarma boshlig&lsquo;i yoki uning o&lsquo;rinbosarlari&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">tomonidan murojaatlarni ko&lsquo;rib chiqishda o&lsquo;zlarining hatti-xarakatlari bilan jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning huquqlarini, erkinliklarini hamda qonuniy manfatlarini, shuningdek, jamiyat va davlat manfaatlarini buzmasligi kerak.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">9-bob. Murojaatlarni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish va bosh boshqarma mansabdor shaxslarining huquq va erkinliklari</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">67. Murojaatlarni ko&lsquo;rib chiqishda&nbsp;&nbsp;Bosh boshqarma&nbsp;&nbsp;mansabdor shaxslari quydagi huquqlarga ega:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 35.45pt 42.55pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish uchun zarur bo&lsquo;lgan axboratni belgilangan tartibda so&lsquo;rash va olish;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 35.45pt 42.55pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">murojaat qiluvchi yoki uning vakilini ular yo&lsquo;qligida murojaatni ko&lsquo;rib chiqish mumkin bo&lsquo;lmaganda yoxud murojaatni eshitish uchun chaqirish;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 35.45pt 42.55pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">bila turib yolg&lsquo;on ma&rsquo;lumot ko&lsquo;rsatilgan murojaatni tekshirish sababli yetkazilgan xarajatlarning o&lsquo;rnini qoplash to&lsquo;g&lsquo;rsida sudga murojaat qilish;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 35.45pt 42.55pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Bosh boshqarma mansabdor shaxslari qonun hujjatlariga muvofiq boshqa huquqlarga ham ega bo&lsquo;lishi mumkin.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">68. Bosh boshqarma mansabdor shaxslari:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"41\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 27.35pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">murojaatlar to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi qonun hujjatlari talablariga rioya etishi;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"41\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 27.35pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">murojaat qiluvchiga uning huquqlari, erkinliklari va qonuniy manfatlariga dahldor hujjatlar, qarorlar va boshqa materiallar bilan tanishib chiqish imkoniyatini, agar ular davlat siri yoki qonun bilan qo&lsquo;riqlanadigan boshqa sir bo&lsquo;lgan ma&rsquo;lumotlarni o&lsquo;z ichiga olmasa, jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning huquqlari, erkinliklari va qonuniy manfatlariga, jamiyat va davlat manfatlariga zarar yetkazmasa, ta&rsquo;minlashi;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"41\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 27.35pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">murojaat etuvchiga ko&lsquo;rib chiqish natijalari hamda qabul qilingan qaror haqida murojaat ko&lsquo;rib chiqilganidan so&lsquo;ng yozma yoxud elektron shaklda darhol xabar qilishi, ommaviy qabul vaqtida tushgan va joyida hal&nbsp;&nbsp;qilingan og&lsquo;zaki murojaatlar bundan mustasno;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"41\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 27.35pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">murojaat yuzasidan qabul qilingan qaror ustidan, agar jismoniy yoki yuridik shaxs ushbu qarorga rozi bo&lsquo;lmasa, shikoyat berish tartibini tushuntirishi;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"41\" style=\"margin-right: 2.0pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">murojaatni&nbsp;&nbsp;ko&lsquo;rib chiqish natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra qabul qilingan qarorning ijrosini nazorat qilishi;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"41\" style=\"margin-right: 2.0pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">qonunga xilof harakatlarni (harakatsizlikni) bartaraf etish yuzasidan darhol chora tadbirlar ko&lsquo;rishi, jismoniy va yuridik shahslarning huquqlari, erkinliklari va qonuniy manfaatlari buzilishini keltirib chiqaruvchi sabablar va sharoitlarni o&lsquo;z vakolatlari doirasida aniqlashi;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"41\" style=\"margin-right: 2.0pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">jismoniy shaxs, uning vakili, ularning oila a&rsquo;zolari, yuridik shaxs, uning vakilining oila a&rsquo;zolari ularning murojaatlari sababli ta&rsquo;qib etilishini belgilangan tartibda bartaraf etishi;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"41\" style=\"margin-right: 2.0pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">agar jismoniy yoki yuridik shaxsga uning huquqlari, erkinliklari hamda qonuniy manfaatlari buzilishi natijasida moddiy zarar yoki ma&rsquo;naviy ziyon yetkazilgan bo&lsquo;lsa, qonunda belgilangan tartibda moddiy zararning o&lsquo;rnini qoplash yoki ma&rsquo;naviy ziyonni kompensatsiya qilish choralari ko&lsquo;rilishi shart.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"41\" style=\"margin-right: 2.0pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"4\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">Bosh boshqarma mansabdor shaxslari qonun hujjatlariga muvofiq boshqa huquqlarga ham ega bo&lsquo;lishi mumkin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"41\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 27.35pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 2.0pt 9.4pt 1.0pt;\"><span class=\"4\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"110\" style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: lines-together; page-break-after: avoid; background: transparent;\"><a name=\"bookmark1\"></a><span class=\"10\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Batang; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-fareast-language: EN-US;\">10</span></span><span class=\"10\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Batang; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">-bob. Murojaatlarning&nbsp;&nbsp;ko&lsquo;rib chikilishini&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">monitoring</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"110\" style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal; mso-pagination: lines-together; page-break-after: avoid; background: transparent;\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">va</span></strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;</span><span clas