di-font-weight: bold;\">qonun hujjatlarini takomillashtirish&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"20\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">yuzasidan&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">takliflar kiritadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"210\" style=\"margin-right: 1.15pt; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.0pt; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"20\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 3.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"210\" style=\"margin-right: 1.15pt; text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.0pt; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"20\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">72. Bosh boshqarma</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;har chorakda O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi Iqtisodiyot vazirligiga murojaatlar bilan&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"20\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">ishlash to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"2\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">hisobot taqdim&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"20\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; font-weight: normal;\">etadi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"line-height: normal; tab-stops: 37.25pt; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\">