ng=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">76. Murojaatlar to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi qonun hujjatlarini buzganlik, huddi shuningdek, tuhmat va xaqoratdan iborat murojaat berganlik belgilangan tartibda javobgarlikka sabab bo&lsquo;ladi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p class=\"140\" style=\"margin-right: 1.15pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"6\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Book Antiqua\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"140\" style=\"margin-right: 1.15pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"6\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Book Antiqua\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Sirdaryo viloyati Iqtisodiy taraqqiyot&nbsp;&nbsp;va kambag&lsquo;allikni</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"140\" style=\"margin-right: 1.15pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"6\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Book Antiqua\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">qisqartirish bosh boshqarmasida&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"60\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"6\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Book Antiqua\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">jismoniy&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"60\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">va&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"6\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Book Antiqua\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">yuridik&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"60\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">shaxslarning</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"140\" style=\"margin-right: 1.15pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"6\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Book Antiqua\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">murojaatlari bilan ishlash tartibi&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"60\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"140\" style=\"margin-right: 1.15pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"60\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 3.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"140\" style=\"margin-right: 1.15pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"14\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">NIZOM</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"140\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"140\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"14\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">1-bob. Umumiy qoidalar</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"line-height: normal; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 1.0pt;\"><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 6.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.45pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Mazkur&nbsp;&nbsp;Nizom (keyingi o&lsquo;rinda Nizom deb ataladi)&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasining</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">2017 yil 11 sentyabrdagi &ldquo;Jismoniy va yuridik&nbsp;&nbsp;shaxslarning&nbsp;&nbsp;murojaatlari&nbsp;&nbsp;to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida&rdquo;gi&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(yangi tahriri)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;O&lsquo;RQ-445-sonli&nbsp;Qonun<span class=\"90\">iga (keyingi o&lsquo;rinlarda Qonun deb ataladi) hamda O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi Vazirlar Maxkamasining 2018 yil 7 maydagi &ldquo;Davlat organlarida, davlat muassasalarida va davlat ishtirokidagi tashkilotlarda jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarining murojaatlari bilan ishlash tartibi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi Namunaviy nizomni tasdiqlash&rdquo; xaqidagi&nbsp;&nbsp;341-sonli qaroriga muvofiq&nbsp;</span><span class=\"6\">Sirdaryo viloyati Iqtisodiyot va sanoat bosh boshqarmasida&nbsp;</span><span class=\"60\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"90\">(keyingi o&lsquo;rinlarda Bosh boshqarma deb ataladi) jismoniy va yuridik shaxslarning murojaatlari bilan ishlash tartibini belgilaydi.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"text-indent: 42.55pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l14 level1 lfo4; background: transparent; margin: 0cm 1.0pt .0001pt 0cm;\"><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">Ushbu Nizomning amal qilishi</span></span><span class=\"90\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black;\">:</span></span><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ko&lsquo;rib chiqish tartibi ma&rsquo;muriy javobgarlik to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidaligi, fuqarolik protsessual, jinoyat-protsessual, iqtisodiy-protsessual qonun hujjatlari va boshqa amaldagi qonunchilik xujjatlari bilan belgilangan murojaatlarga;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;davlat organlarining, tashkilotlarining, shuningdek ular tarkibiy bo&lsquo;linmalarining o&lsquo;zaro yozishmalariga nisbatan tatbiq etilmaydi.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">3. Qonunga muvofiq ushbu Nizomda quyidagi asosiy tushunchalar qo&lsquo;llaniladi:&nbsp;<strong>ariza</strong>&nbsp;- huquqlarni, erkinliklarni va qonuniy manfaatlarni amalga oshirishda yordam ko&lsquo;rsatish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi iltimos bayon etilgan murojaat;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"90\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">taklif&nbsp;</span></strong></span><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">- davlat va jamiyat faoliyatini takomillashtirishga doir tavsiyalarni o&lsquo;z ichiga olgan murojaat;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"90\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">shikoyat</span></strong></span><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;- buzilgan huquqlarni, erkinliklarni tiklash va qonuniy manfaatlarni himoya qilish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi talab bayon etilgan murojaat;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"90\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">elektron murojaat</span></strong></span><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;- belgilangan tartibda axborot-kommunikatsiya texnologiyalari vositasida berilgan, shu jumladan davlat organining, tashkilotning rasmiy veb-saytiga joylashtirilgan murojaat, real vaqt rejimida axborot-kommunikatsiya texnologiyalaridan foydalangan holda berilgan og&lsquo;zaki murojaatlar bundan mustasno;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"90\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">takroriy murojaat</span></strong></span><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;- ayni bir jismoniy yoki yuridik shaxsdan kelib tushgan, uning avvalgi murojaati yuzasidan qabul qilingan qaror ustidan shikoyat qilinayotgan yoki boshqacha tarzda norozilik bildirilayotgan, shuningdek, agar takroriy murojaat kelib tushgan paytga kelib qonunchilikda belgilangan ko&lsquo;rib chiqish muddati tugagan bo&lsquo;lsa, ilgarigi murojaati o&lsquo;z vaqtida ko&lsquo;rib chiqilmaganligi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida xabar qilinayotgan murojaat;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"90\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">anonim murojaat</span></strong></span><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;- jismoniy shaxsning familiyasi (ismi, otasining ismi), uning yashash joyi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi ma&rsquo;lumotlar yoki yuridik shaxsning to&lsquo;liq nomi, uning joylashgan yeri (pochta manzili) to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi ma&rsquo;lumotlar ko&lsquo;rsatilmagan yoxud ular haqida yolg&lsquo;on ma&rsquo;lumotlar ko&lsquo;rsatilgan murojaat, shuningdek uni identifikatsiya qilish imkoniyatini bermaydigan elektron murojaat yoxud imzo bilan tasdiqlanmagan yozma murojaat;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"90\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">murojaatning dublikati</span></strong></span><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;- ayni bir jismoniy yoki yuridik shaxs murojaatining ko&lsquo;chirma nusxasi;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"90\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">ommaviy qabul</span></strong></span><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;- davlat organi rahbarining yoki bu borada vakolat berilgan mansabdor shaxsining jismoniy shaxslar va yuridik shaxslarning vakillari bilan ommaviy uchrashuvlarida murojaatlarni qabul qilishga doir harakati;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"90\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">videokonferensaloqa</span></strong></span><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;- uzoqda joylashgan bir nechta abonentlarning real vaqt rejimida audio- va videoaxborot almashish imkoniyati bilan axborot-kommunikatsiya texnologiyalaridan foydalangan holda interaktiv hamkorlik qilishi;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"91\" style=\"margin-right: 1.0pt; text-indent: 35.4pt; line-height: normal; background: transparent;\"><span class=\"90\"><strong><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">davlat ishtirokidagi tashkilot</span></strong></span><span class=\"90\"><span lang=\"UZ-CYR\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; color: black; mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;\">&nbsp;- ustav fondida davlat ulushi mavjud bo&lsquo;lgan tijorat tashkiloti yoxud to&lsquo;liq yoki qisman davlat 